<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="M" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Misty" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Misty,</orth> overspread with mist; cloudy: <cit><quote>m. vapours when they blot the sky,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ven 184" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 184</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. luc 782" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 782</bibl>. <cit><quote>m. night covers the shame,</quote> <bibl n="shak. luc 782" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 782</bibl></cit> <cit><quote>from their m. jaws breathe foul contagious darkness,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 4.1.6" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B IV, 1, 6</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>Cocytus' m. mouth,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tit 2.3.236" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. II, 3, 236</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>m. vale,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tit 5.2.36" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 2, 36</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>on the m. mountain tops,</quote> <bibl n="shak. rom 3.5.10" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. III, 5, 10</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>